name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: 10 Blue Links - Remove Google AI summaries

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically remove AI summaries from Google search by adding the `udm=14` parameter.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tired of AI summaries that return unreliable information in Google search results? 

10 Blue Links will help you reclaim your search experience by automatically switching to “Web” results. 

The extension works by adding “&udm=14” to every Google search query. This special parameter tells Google to display only the classic “10 blue links” search results, without AI-generated summaries and other cruft. 

Instead, you get clean, focused results with only the most relevant websites, helping you find what you need.
